						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the platform of the <hi rend="italic">dhvajastaṁbha</hi> in the Śiva temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Nandana, Jyēshṭha śu. 12.</p>						

						<p>Records the setting up of the <hi rend="italic">dhvajastaṁbha</hi> in the Īśvara temple at Mallelakuṁṭa by <hi rend="italic">Karaṇaṁ</hi> Veṅkaṭarāvu, son of Chinna Subbarāo of Peddajūṭūru. Further, it mentions Chinnappōḍu and Venkaṭanna, who cast the <hi rend="italic">dhvajastaṁbha.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
